::The Galactors/FZ::

The Galactors land near FZ.

"Commander," Supernova reports, "We've come upon a functional bot on 
our search for DNA. You might want to see this."

FZ turns around, his eyes widening when he sees the scrapped 
Wolfgang. He hadn't expected to see Wolfgang after the Alliance had 
scrapped him and left him for dead, and this was quite a surprise.

"Interesting.." FZ says, "Allright, take him to the CRs, I'll join 
you shortly."

FZ walks down a hallway, heading for Zardus as the Galactors set off 
toward the CR chambers.
